format

public String format()
Returns the persistent identifier of a process instance in the EBX5 repository.

Compared to the method getId(), this identifier takes into account the publication key.

Since:
5.5.1

getId

public int getId()
Returns the identifier of a process instance, in the scope of its published process definition. Namely, it is unique regarding all process instances associated with a given published process definition, but not unique in the context of the EBX5 repository.
